---
import Breadcrumbs from '@/components/breadcrumbs.astro'
import PageHead from '@/components/page-head.astro'
import Layout from '@/layouts/layout.astro'
---

<Layout class="max-w-3xl">
  <PageHead slot="head" title="Uses" />
  <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Uses', icon: 'lucide:info' }]} />

  <section>
    <div class="min-w-full">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-black font-cooper m-0">Uses</h1>
      <div class="prose mb-8">
        <p>
          <b>Tools and tech I use.</b> Here are some of them.
        </p>
        <h3>At my desk</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc" style="margin-left: 2rem;">
          <li><a href="https://www.fnac.pt/Portatil-Gaming-OMEN-by-HP-15-dc0035np-Computador-Portatil-Computador-Portatil-Gaming/a6474112">OMEN by HP 15-dc0035np</a>, my daily driver running <a href="https://garudalinux.org/">Garuda Linux</a>, nicknamed <a href="https://yokai.com/kinko-gold/">kinko</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://www.lenovo.com/us/en/p/laptops/thinkpad/thinkpadt/thinkpad-t460/22tp2tt4600">ThinkPad T460</a>, my <a href="https://i.kym-cdn.com/editorials/icons/mobile/000/001/508/hackerman-icon.jpg">hackerman</a> laptop running <a href="https://fedoraproject.org/">Fedora 43</a>, nicknamed <a href="https://yokai.com/isogashi/">isogashi</a></li>
          <li><a href="https://electronics.sony.com/audio/headphones/headband/p/wh1000xm4-b">Sony WH-1000XM4</a>, wireless noise-cancelling headphones</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.razer.com/gaming-mice/razer-orochi-v2">Razer Orochi V2</a>, wireless mouse</li>
          <li><a href="https://en.sharkoon.com/product/SGK50S4">Sharkoon SKILLER SGK50 S4</a>, mechanical keyboard</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.ikea.com/pt/pt/p/markus-cadeira-giratoria-vissle-cinz-esc-70261150/">IKEA MARKUS</a>, office chair</li>
        </ul>
        <hr/>
        <h2>On my laptop</h2>
        <h3>Communication</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc" style="margin-left: 2rem;">
          <li><a href="https://discord.com/">Discord</a>, chat and communities</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.whatsapp.com/">WhatsApp Web</a>, family chat</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Dev environment</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc" style="margin-left: 2rem;">
          <li><a href="https://alacritty.org/">Alacritty</a>, terminal</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.jetbrains.com/lp/mono/">JetBrains Mono</a>, terminal font</li>
          <li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bash_(Unix_shell)">Bash</a>, shell</li>
          <li><a href="https://code.visualstudio.com/">Visual Studio Code</a>, editor</li>
          <li><a href="https://i3wm.org/">i3</a>, window manager</li>
          <li><a href="https://archlinux.org/pacman/">Pacman</a>, package manager (kinko)</li>
          <li><a href="https://dnf.readthedocs.io/">DNF</a>, package manager (isogashi)</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>File management</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc" style="margin-left: 2rem;">
          <li><a href="https://infinitedigits.co/croc/">croc</a>, secure file transfer between two computers</li>
          <li><a href="https://localsend.org/">LocalSend</a>, cross-platform AirDrop alternative</li>
          <li><a href="https://syncthing.net/">Syncthing</a>, continuous file synchronization</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Multimedia</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc" style="margin-left: 2rem;">
          <li><a href="https://spotify.com">Spotify</a>, music player</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.videolan.org/vlc/">VLC</a>, video player</li>
          <li><a href="https://rawtherapee.com/">RawTherapee</a>, free cross-platform raw image processor</li>
          <li><a href="https://github.com/CyberTimon/RapidRAW">RapidRAW</a>, modern high-performance Lightroom alternative</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Office</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc" style="margin-left: 2rem;">
          <li><a href="https://drive.google.com/">Google Drive</a>, office suite</li>
          <li><a href="https://meet.google.com/">Google Meet</a>, online meetings</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Productivity</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc" style="margin-left: 2rem;">
          <li><a href="https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/">Firefox</a>, web browser</li>
          <li><a href="https://obsidian.md/">Obsidian</a>, personal knowledge base</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Security</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc" style="margin-left: 2rem;">
          <li><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Google_Authenticator">Google Authenticator</a>, 2FA authenticator</li>
          <li><a href="https://bitwarden.com/">Bitwarden</a>, password manager</li>
        </ul>
        <hr/>
        <h2>Photography gear</h2>
        <h3>Cameras</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc" style="margin-left: 2rem;">
          <li><a href="https://us.ricoh-imaging.com/product/pentax-17/">Pentax 17</a>, half-frame 35mm film camera</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.canon.co.uk/cameras/eos-250d/">Canon EOS 250D</a>, entry-level DSLR</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>Lenses</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc" style="margin-left: 2rem;">
          <li><a href="https://www.canon.co.uk/lenses/ef-s-18-55mm-f-3-5-5-6-is-ii-lens/">Canon EF-S 18-55mm f/3.5-5.6</a>, kit zoom lens</li>
          <li><a href="https://www.canon.co.uk/lenses/ef-50mm-f-1-8-stm-lens/">Canon EF 50mm f/1.8 STM</a>, nifty fifty prime lens</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">Last modified: <b>6 April 2026</b></p>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm">Inspired by <a href="https://uses.tech/">uses.tech</a>.</p>
        <hr/>
        <h2>Changelog</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-4">
          <li>
            06 April 2026 - v1.0
            <div>Initial version.</div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2,
  .prose h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-cooper);
  }
</style>
